## functions.php — important notes

DO NOT modify without asking Matt:
- dashboard_fixes.php include
- Block auto-registration loop
- jQuery replacement decision

Safe to modify:
- Enqueue section (uncomment plugins per project)
- Menu registration
- boilerplate_theme_support()
- boilerplate_create_starter_pages()

