## JS plugins — commented out by default

Uncomment in functions.php per project as needed:

| Plugin | Use case | File path |
|---|---|---|
| Owl Carousel | Gallery block — already active in V3 | `~js_plugins/owl-carousel/` |
| Lightbox | Image lightboxes | `~js_plugins/lightbox/` |
| Lity | Inline lightboxes | `~js_plugins/lity/` |
| FitVids | Responsive video embeds | `~js_plugins/fitVids/` |

